OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778054737
OL,3,CArsenal ready to play like 'beasts',
OL,4,CMikel Arteta warns Atletico Madrid
OL,6,FBut, speaking on the eve of Arsenal's
OL,7,Fdecisive European clash in London `
OL,8,Fwith either Paris St Germain or Bayern
OL,9,FMunich waiting in the final ` Arteta
OL,10,Fsaid: "We will take to the pitch as
OL,11,Fbeasts tomorrow and enjoy the moment
OL,12,Fand go for it.
OL,14,F"I can't wait. I feel the energy among
OL,15,Fthe team and our supporters. This is
OL,16,Fthe moment that we want to live
OL,17,Ftogether. We have worked hard as a
OL,18,Fclub and as a team after 20 years to
OL,19,Fbe in this position again. And we are
OL,20,Fso hungry to get through to that final.
OL,26,@rD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778054737
OL,3,CArsenal ready to play like 'beasts',
OL,4,CMikel Arteta warns Atletico Madrid
OL,6,F"It is a feeling of huge excitement.
OL,7,FIt's difficult to express the desire
OL,8,Fto live that moment, especially with
OL,9,Four people in front of us.
OL,11,F"They've been waiting for so long to
OL,12,Fhave this kind of night. So let's push
OL,13,Fhard tomorrow, because something
OL,14,Famazing is going to happen."
OL,16,FArteta will be boosted by the
OL,17,Favailability of captain Martin
OL,18,FOdegaard, absent from his side's win
OL,19,Fagainst Fulham, and also Kai Havertz,
OL,20,Fwho has missed the past two games with
OL,21,Fa knee injury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
