OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778054737
OL,3,CArsenal ready to play like 'beasts',
OL,4,CMikel Arteta warns Atletico Madrid
OL,6,FArsenal last appeared in a Champions
OL,7,FLeague final in 2006 ` a 2-1 defeat to
OL,8,FBarcelona ` and the north London club
OL,9,Fhave never won Europe's grandest
OL,10,Fcompetition.
OL,12,FHowever, when asked if he could
OL,13,Fvisualise Odegaard lifting the famous
OL,14,Ftrophy later this month, Arteta, who
OL,15,Fhas been manager of Arsenal since
OL,16,F2019, continued: "I did that many
OL,17,Fyears ago and it was the thing that I
OL,18,Fhad in mind for this club.
OL,26,@xD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778054737
OL,3,CArsenal ready to play like 'beasts',
OL,4,CMikel Arteta warns Atletico Madrid
OL,6,F"You can never promise to win major
OL,7,Ftrophies, but you can promise to work
OL,8,Fevery single day by implementing the
OL,9,Fvision and being determined with the
OL,10,Fideas and the decisions to make this
OL,11,Fclub one of the best in Europe. Here
OL,12,Fwe are. Now we have to make the next
OL,13,Fstep."
OL,15,FUnlike at this stage last season,
OL,16,FArteta resisted the urge to call on
OL,17,Fhis supporters to "bring their boots
OL,18,Fand kick every ball" in order to carry
OL,19,Ftheir side to the final, which this
OL,20,Fyear will be staged in Budapest on May
OL,21,F30.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@SOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
