OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1778054737
OL,3,CArsenal ready to play like 'beasts',
OL,4,CMikel Arteta warns Atletico Madrid
OL,6,FBut the Arsenal manager said he is
OL,7,Fexpecting a hostile atmosphere for
OL,8,Fwhat will be his team's penultimate
OL,9,Fgame at home in a season they hope
OL,10,Fwill end with two trophies.
OL,12,F"I don't think a message (to the fans)
OL,13,Fis needed," added Arteta. "It's what
OL,14,Fis at stake that says it all.
OL,16,F"But I can't wait to live this moment
OL,17,Fwith our supporters, our people and
OL,18,Fgenerate something really, really
OL,19,Fspecial to get into that final. Let's
OL,20,Flive this together, go grab it and
OL,21,Flet's make it happen."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@KO]uD@[OUxD@AOU}D@VO]
